<bibRefCitation author="Wrase DW" box="[416,560,1152,1179]" journalOrPublisher="Linzer biologische Beitrage" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="807 - 813" part="37" refId="ref3956" refString="Wrase DW (2005) Description of a new Philorhizus species from Greece and faunistic notes on other species previously described (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Lebiini). Linzer biologische Beitrage 37 (1): 807 - 813." title="Description of a new Philorhizus species from Greece and faunistic notes on other species previously described (Coleoptera, Carabidae, Lebiini)" type="journal article" year="2005">Wrase 2005</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
